longBusinessSummary: Kingbo Strike Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the supply and installation of solar photovoltaic parts and equipment; and electrical distribution system business in the People's Republic of China and Singapore. It operates through three segments: Solar Power Business, Electrical Distribution System, and Electrical Engineering Services. The company supplies and installs electrical distribution systems, including distribution board, junction box, cables and switches, etc. In addition, it is involved in the provision of finance; and electrical and general building engineering services. Kingbo Strike Limited was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Kowloon, Hong Kong.
